Forts.: 12 Septbr 1885
plenty thanks for the news of your arrival For after the little bit of
Carls forgetfulness we doubted whether he had not dropped you somewhere on
the road, or had slipped out of your hands. Nothing changed here. At times
the mind of Omama is clear and also accessible to comfort. She thinks it is
a very long time and a strange trial, but smiled, when reminded of Uranies
time, which the latter now will think a moment. Ask your dear Oncle Hesse
if he has the newest proceedings of the Church Mission ....611
